WEBVTT

00:00.040 --> 00:03.280
We've been using coterie diapers and wipes for so long now,

00:03.281 --> 00:06.001
so I'm so excited they came out with this swimsuit.

00:06.002 --> 00:08.001
It's made with safe ingredients.

00:08.002 --> 00:09.021
No fragrances,

00:09.080 --> 00:12.360
no parabens, and it has a very elastic waistband

00:12.361 --> 00:14.941
to where my toddlers don't feel suffocated.

00:15.440 --> 00:16.560
Another thing that I like

00:16.561 --> 00:18.481
in comparison to other swim diapers

00:18.482 --> 00:21.161
is that they don't balloon up when they're in the water,

00:21.162 --> 00:22.730
so they love wearing them.
